## ✨ Features

### 📝 Essay Management
- **Create & Edit Essays**: Write and save college essays with rich text editing
- **Categories**: Organize essays by type (Personal Statement, Supplemental, Scholarship, Other)
- **College Assignment**: Assign essays to specific colleges you're applying to
- **Word Count**: Real-time word counting for each essay
- **Deadlines**: Set and track essay deadlines
- **Draft Saving**: Save work-in-progress essays as drafts
- **Drag & Drop**: Drag essays between colleges for easy organization

### 🤖 AI Writing Assistant
- **Smart Analysis**: AI analyzes your essay content and provides specific feedback
- **Writing Suggestions**: Get suggestions for improving clarity, engagement, and style
- **Grammar Check**: Automated grammar and style checking
- **One-Click Improvements**: Apply AI suggestions with a single click
- **Interactive Chat**: Chat with AI for brainstorming and writing help
- **Context-Aware**: AI understands your essay category and provides relevant advice

### 🏫 College Management
- **Add Colleges**: Create profiles for each college you're applying to
- **Application Status**: Track whether you've started, submitted, or received decisions
- **Status Filtering**: Filter colleges by application status
- **Progress Tracking**: Visual progress bars and status indicators
- **College Details**: Store location, deadlines, and notes for each college

### 📊 Statistics Dashboard
- **Overview Stats**: Total essays, words, completed essays, average words per essay
- **Category Breakdown**: Visual representation of essays by category
- **College Breakdown**: See how many essays you have for each college
- **Progress Tracking**: Monitor your writing progress

### 💾 Data Management
- **Local Storage**: All essays are saved locally in your browser
- **Export**: Export all essays as JSON file for backup
- **Import**: Import previously exported essays
- **Auto-save**: Automatic saving of essay data

### 🎨 Modern UI/UX
- **Responsive Design**: Works perfectly on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- **Beautiful Interface**: Modern gradient design with smooth animations
- **Intuitive Navigation**: Easy-to-use navigation between sections
- **Modal Views**: Clean essay viewing and editing experience
- **Drag & Drop Interface**: Intuitive essay organization by college

