## 📖 How to Use

### Getting Started
1. Open the application in your web browser
2. Click "Colleges" to add the colleges you're applying to
3. Click "New Essay" to create your first essay
4. Assign essays to colleges using the dropdown or drag & drop
5. Use "My Essays" to view and organize all your essays

### Creating Essays
1. Navigate to "New Essay" section
2. Enter essay title and select category
3. Optionally set a deadline and assign to a college
4. Write your essay content
5. Click "Save Essay" to save

### Using AI Assistant
1. Click "AI Writing Assistant" while writing
2. Use quick prompts or ask custom questions
3. Get specific suggestions for your essay
4. Apply improvements with one click

### Managing Colleges
- **Add Colleges**: Click "Add College" to add colleges you're applying to
- **Edit Colleges**: Click the edit button on any college card to modify details
- **Delete Colleges**: Click the delete button to remove colleges (essays will be unassigned)
- **Track Status**: Update application status as you progress

### Managing Essays
- **View Essays**: Click on any essay card to view full content
- **Edit**: Click "Edit" in the essay modal to modify
- **Delete**: Click "Delete" in the essay modal to remove
- **Assign to College**: Use the college dropdown when creating/editing essays
- **Drag & Drop**: Drag essays from "My Essays" to college cards to assign them
- **Search**: Use the search bar to find specific essays
- **Filter**: Use category and college filters to organize essays

